# Ignore everything
*

# But allow directory traversal
!*/

# Track these files
!.gitignore
!.env.example
!**/app.cob
!**/*.cpy
!README.md
!.github/
!.github/**

# Never track secrets and build artifacts
.env
*.exe
*.csv
*.json
*.tmp
*.log
*.time

# Belt-and-suspenders: explicit per-file patterns for S05E03 runtime
# artifacts that contain HUB_API_KEY or other sensitive payloads. The
# blanket "*" above already covers these, but listing them explicitly
# protects against future allow-list rules (e.g. "!*.log") that would
# otherwise expose cached hub request/response bodies.
S05E03/hub_req.tmp
S05E03/hub_resp.json
S05E03/llm_req.json
S05E03/llm_resp.json
S05E03/work.tmp
S05E03/run*.log
S05E03/run*.time
S05E03/app.exe

# But allow specific data files needed by tasks
!S01E01/suspects.json
!S01E03/Containerfile
!S01E03/start.sh
!copybooks/*
